@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zbjray(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.abs((tmp + 0.30 + v1 + 0.95)))
    v0 = v1
    tmp = v1
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.90)) / ((v2 + 0.12 / tmp + 0.47) / wp.exp(v2 + 0.23)))
    data[tid] = v0
